{"tid":735054,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求耳科推介","createTime":"2018-07-09T07:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:36:50.000Z","uid":172889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"540b2c4dfc6b8a83fbb9f8d02ac8bc0f1ad75061","tid":735054,"uid":172889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"求耳科推介<br />\n上星期去完旅行, 坐回程機返香港時班機因落唔到機場係空中兜咗幾個圈<br />\n兜圈時我左耳有D 唔舒服之後落到地幾日都頭暈暈, 腳步浮浮, 個人唔係好集中<br />\n上網睇資料有教人做耳石復位法<br />\n做咗一兩日有好轉, 但都仲係未消除頭暈, 隻耳仲係有少少奇怪感(未去到耳塞聽唔到嘢嗰隻)<br />\n<br />\n想跪求好醫生推介<br />\n而家個感覺唔太好, 做嘢好難集中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48701101e133b8511af9936a5c5bbfa45a795a4","tid":735054,"uid":172889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}